name: S-64 Skycrane™
description: Capable of carrying over 20,000 lbs., the Sikorsky Skycrane™ is one of the strongest heavy-lifting helicopters in the world. A firefighting workhorse, the Skycrane™ can also be fitted to hold 2,650 gallons of water – which it can refill with its hydraulic snorkel system in 45 seconds!
